# D{{N}} — External Systems Landscape

**Audience:** Stakeholder + Architect (integration scoping conversations).
**When to look at this:** Before signing a partner contract, before estimating an integration, when the security team asks "what data leaves our boundary?".
**Prose gap closed:** Each canvas's § Inbound / § Outbound communication lists external touchpoints in isolation; this diagram shows the **whole boundary** in one frame at C4 Level 1.

---

## What sits outside {{SYSTEM_NAME}} and how data flows across the boundary

```mermaid
C4Context
    title {{PROJECT_NAME}} — System Context (C4 Level 1)

    {{#PERSONS}}
    Person({{id}}, "{{label}}", "{{description}}")
    {{/PERSONS}}

    System({{system_id}}, "{{SYSTEM_NAME}}", "{{SYSTEM_DESCRIPTION}}")

    {{#EXT_SYSTEMS}}
    System_Ext({{id}}, "{{label}}", "{{description}}")
    {{/EXT_SYSTEMS}}

    {{#REL_IN}}
    Rel({{from_id}}, {{system_id}}, "{{label}}")
    {{/REL_IN}}

    {{#REL_OUT}}
    Rel({{system_id}}, {{to_id}}, "{{label}}")
    {{/REL_OUT}}

    {{#REL_BIDIR}}
    BiRel({{system_id}}, {{other_id}}, "{{label}}")
    {{/REL_BIDIR}}

    UpdateLayoutConfig($c4ShapeInRow="3", $c4BoundaryInRow="1")
```

