## Legend (C4 conventions)

| Box style | Meaning |
|-----------|---------|
| Person (yellow figure) | Human role outside the system boundary |
| System (blue box) | The system being designed |
| System_Ext (grey box) | External system the design depends on |
| Rel (solid arrow) | Single-direction dependency, labelled with protocol |
| BiRel (double arrow) | Bidirectional dependency |

C4 styling is controlled by the C4Context block itself — colors are
canonical to the C4 model and should not be overridden.

